com.io7m.r2.core

Class R2TransformSiOT

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.io7m.r2.core.R2TransformSiOT
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    R2TransformNonOrthogonalReadableType, R2TransformReadableType, R2TransformType

    public final class R2TransformSiOT
extends Object
implements R2TransformNonOrthogonalReadableType, R2TransformType

    A transform represented by a scale, followed by an orientation, followed by a translation.

    The transform allows independent scaling on each axis and may therefore produce matrices that are not orthogonal.
